.. activecode:: ab_5

    Write a program that asks the user for number of days. Calculate, then print out, the user's input as 
    number of years, months and days.  Assume each month is 30 days and each year is 365 days.

    Ex. If user enters "431", your program should print out "1 year, 2 months, and 6 days."

    ~~~~
    